pkg
===

Git-based package system. 

Package structure
==================
* $dev - packages directory
  * package_name - package directory
    * shr - directory with shared files
    * app - application specific files to be saved into separated directory
    * exe - executable files directory
    * dep - dependencies directory
      * pkg
      * Linux
        * void
        * debian
        * arch
      * OpenBSD
      * FreeBSD
      * NetBSD
    * build - executable file to run before installation (it should set up shr, app and exe dirs)

